@node Server Internals
@chapter Server Internals
@cindex internals
@cindex architecture

This chapter is the operator-and-developer reference for how the server
fits together: process model, request lifecycle, the database schema,
the embedding-provider abstraction, the security model, logging, and
how the auto-migration framework handles schema changes over time.

